ception of the wine's freshness.\n\n**Marketing and Sales**:\n- The demand for Domaine bottles may increase currently.\n- Priced steadily despite aiming for higher transparency in product design and target market positioning. The strategy encompasses creating an affordable yet sustainable product to facilitate enterprise growth and improvement.\n\n---\n\nThe document appears to be from a section of a graduate thesis by Gabrielle Valentin, focusing on safety regulations in agricultural settings and the sustainable, biodynamic approaches in winemaking at a specific vineyard, Domaine des Ruissons."
